{"tid":1815711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隻武漢肺炎除左武漢同香港(疑似個案)有出現，鄰國其他城市好似無出現咁既??","createTime":"2020-01-07T17:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T02:28:05.000Z","uid":62011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f597c014da0066b0b06424c237aec9ba1c04ab90","tid":1815711,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/20/1/4/n11766872.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fgb%2F20%2F1%2F4%2Fn11766872.htm&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=c101d1bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/20/1/4/n11766872.htm</a><br />\n(大紀元話武漢有肺炎、其他城市有其他傳染病)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51005004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51005004&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=e34858be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51005004&h=826c7c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51005004</a><br />\n(BBC話除武漢外，暫未有中國內地其他省市公布「不明原因肺炎」案例。)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200106-mainland-wuhan-pneumonia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200106-mainland-wuhan-pneumonia%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=87964ccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200106-mainland-wuhan-pneumonia/</a><br />\n(端傳媒話除武漢外，暫未有內地其他省市公佈不明原因肺炎案例。)<br />\n<br />\n我有搵過twitter同其他媒體，都無咩描寫到其他城市有肺炎個案。<br />\n<br />\n暫時黎講，除左武漢、香港(疑似個案)。鄰國其他城市無? <br />\n<br />\n係真係無&gt;? 定封鎖消息? 定係我漏左其他新聞有講?<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901f02dce9c85d3a455b9c6157a6972c60a2945f","tid":1815711,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"香港有<br />\n武漢有<br />\n<br />\n中間既唔見哂<br />\n<br />\n講都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbc299bb50854b28fb4f8e62f82448122b29bc6","tid":1815711,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"早兩日好似話星加坡有疑似個案，個細路女去過武漢<br />\n<br />\n支那你就唔好EXPECT有咩新聞啦<br />\n有都唔會報啦"},{"pid":"d2acd013d1b87bc6c1deac1efd2f43accc811fec","tid":1815711,"uid":2053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:49:48.000Z","msg":"大陸封鎖消息就梗㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />基本上所有消息傳播媒介都係中共嘅控制之下，佢的起心肝要封鎖消息，就算上面死左成千萬人你都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc0dda71eb35fb463bf0fab750613794efd9b9f","tid":1815711,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:52:27.000Z","msg":"武漢有<br />\n香港有<br />\n台灣有<br />\n新加坡有<br />\n<br />\n中國境內其他地方冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea24b9994ed1ed950088b1c4c3f0647b2448726f","tid":1815711,"uid":52085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:54:37.000Z","msg":"武漢同香港隔咗幾多個城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf7101d